<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- (lwlạ mwt ạlṣlb yạ fạdy .. lwlạ ḥbk wqt ʿnạdy
 ʿnd ṣlybk ṣwt bynạdy .. ṣwt ykẖly ạlqlb yqwl)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̹nt nwry ạ̹nt nwry)2
 (ạ̹nt nwry wkl ḥyạty)2
 2- (myn kạn gẖyrk ymḥy ạ̉tẖạmy .. yḥml ʿạry wynhy ậlạmy
 myn kạn gẖyrk ysẖfy sqạmy .. myn ykẖly ạlqlb yqwl)2
 3- (ạ̹tḥmlt ạlṣlb bdạly .. kạn ạldm ạltmn ạlgẖạly
 ṭhr qlby wgẖyr ḥạly .. kẖly̱ ṣwt ạlqlb yqwl)2
 4- (mhmạ ạ̉tklm wạlqy̱ mʿạny .. wyrddhạ bṣwty lsạny
 yʿjz wṣfy wkl kyạny .. yrjʿ ṣwt ạlqlb yqwl)2</lyrics>
<title>lwlạ mwt ạlṣlb</title>
